I know.

259
00:20:15,416 --> 00:20:16,583
Let's do it!

260
00:20:25,583 --> 00:20:28,083
Why do they keep
trying the same maneuver?

261
00:20:46,458 --> 00:20:47,375
[NAMENBA]
There it is!

262
00:20:47,458 --> 00:20:49,375
The signal! It's time!

263
00:20:55,375 --> 00:20:57,000
Stupid little primate!

264
00:20:57,083 --> 00:20:58,458
Just like I thought!

265
00:20:58,541 --> 00:21:00,708
Whenever he uses his
technique, there's a gap

266
00:21:00,791 --> 00:21:02,833
before he can pull it off again!

267
00:21:02,916 --> 00:21:03,833
Namenba!

268
00:21:03,916 --> 00:21:06,208
Four Twelve, Kite!

269
00:21:06,291 --> 00:21:07,250
[gasps]

270
00:21:09,916 --> 00:21:11,416
The stars are vanishing!

271
00:21:11,500 --> 00:21:12,708
How strange.

272
00:21:12,791 --> 00:21:13,916
[SAIZOU]
Heh.

273
00:21:17,166 --> 00:21:18,125
[gasps]

274
00:21:32,916 --> 00:21:34,125
[gas[s]

275
00:21:42,458 --> 00:21:44,208
Now, let's get moving!

276
00:23:43,458 --> 00:23:46,041
[NARRATOR] Once more,
the demon begins to grow.

277
00:23:46,125 --> 00:23:48,833
Deep within the tunnel,
Higurashi Shichigen sees

278
00:23:48,916 --> 00:23:51,375
a memory of his mother.

279
00:23:51,458 --> 00:23:53,166
He sees the truth.

280
00:23:53,250 --> 00:23:55,708
And Hibiki, you...

